  npcName: Fisherman Joe
  npcPortrait: {fileID: -3663117883524363142, guid: 87b7217ab79884d4a8d63bf6fe30eb77, type: 3}
  dialogueLines:
  - ARRRRGHHHHHHHHH- ok thats a bit old fashioned gobbledyegook.
  - Hey there sailor! My name is joe, I will be assisting your sweep for this evening
  - Ever since we started studying aquatic life, we have developed a way to safely
    rid of trash, recycle it..
  - At the same time, do it safely without hurting the underwater environment.
  - We use a non-lethal laser- well I wouldn't say NON-LETHAL... just becareful where
    you aim
  - Anyways, the laser melts down any type of plastic or metallic waste into oil,
    converting it into a source of fuel.
  - Here in this company, we have been using this method for quite a while now so
    you will be able to do the same things for the sake of safety for the aquatic
    life.
  - Again, careful where you aim
  autoProgressLines: 0101010101010101
